Invocation Name: zien hong
des:
Zien Hong is a Chinese and Vietnamese restaurant located in Portland, Oregon.

You can find out what some of the popular dishes are on our menu, our address, and open and close times.

Also find out what our daily specials are!

Some questions you can ask are:

What's on your menu?

What are your house specials?

Tell me today's specials.

What are your lunch specials?

What's Zien Hong's address?

What time are you open tomorrow?

What's your phone number?
